name: Rasta Tee
description:
An ultra soft tie dye tee shirt for extra comfort and style. Dyed and set using professional tie dye techniques. This means that the dye will not run or fade in the wash.

Please Note* 
Each tie dye is hand made for each specific order. This means that every tie dye is completely unique. Please leave 2 days to allow for dyeing, all orders placed before 12 noon dyed same day.
